<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6758442>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Photographs of live Cephalaspidea species: (a) The alien Haloa japonica. (b) Haminoea orteai. (c) Egg mass of Haminoea orteai. (d) Philine catena. The Nudibranchia species: (e) Aegires palensis. (f) White morphotype of Aegires sublaevis. (g) Aldisa smaragdina on top of the sponge Phorbas topsenti. (h) Okenia longiductis on the bryozoan Amathia verticillata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6758442/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

